snippet.title: CRAZY CATS vs PAPER, get ready for SUPER LAUGHING! - Funny CAT VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Funny cats and kittens are the best and funniest animals ever! They make us laugh all the time! This funny cat compilation is a super hard TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge! Just look how all these cats play with paper! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
